16:58.470 --> 17:00.310
Saya dah lapor polis demi cari awak.

17:00.350 --> 17:01.160
Awak tahukah?

17:01.190 --> 17:01.910
Namun...

17:02.500 --> 17:03.590
Ayah awak cakap

17:04.390 --> 17:05.250
jika

17:05.609 --> 17:07.369
saya berani cari awak secara peribadi lagi...

17:09.780 --> 17:10.460
