23:41.870 --> 23:43.210
Kenapa awak muncul di sini?

23:44.460 --> 23:45.970
Dia sangat merindui awak.

23:46.180 --> 23:47.490
Saya takut dia ada keberbahayaan

23:47.720 --> 23:48.870
