28:38.230 --> 28:39.270
dia pasti akan terima awak.

28:40.470 --> 28:41.420
Jangan menangis lagi.

28:41.590 --> 28:42.210
Tengoklah.

28:42.250 --> 28:43.480
Tengoklah, awak menangis lagi.

28:46.110 --> 28:47.150
Awak laparkah?

28:47.320 --> 28:47.930
Lapar.

28:48.550 --> 28:49.210
Saya masak bubur?

28:50.920 --> 28:51.660
